definitions.definition: An object that has undergone preliminary shaping but is not yet in its final form.
The rough, incomplete and unused basic form of a stone tool.
A word that is no longer in use, but has been reconstructed from current ones.

main_definition: An object that has undergone preliminary shaping but is not yet in its final form.
secondary_definitions: ( archaeology ) The rough, incomplete and unused basic form of a stone tool.
